HEADWORD: Intermobility
<hw>In`ter*mo*bil"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Capacity of
things to move among each other; <as>as, the <ex>intermobility</ex> of
fluid particles</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
